<p class=3D"xisselectedend">Hi,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend">I am writing to follow up on my previous request=
s, as I have not yet received an acknowledgement or response regarding the r=
efund of my accommodation expenses.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend">Under the policy coverage of NZD 30,000, there i=
s still a remaining balance of&nbsp;<strong><span style=3D"font-family:&quot=
;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">NZD 1,820.62</span></strong>. However, reimbursemen=
t has only been provided up to&nbsp;<strong><span style=3D"font-family:&quot=
;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">20
 November</span></strong>, leaving the remaining amount outstanding.<o:p></o=
:p></p>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend">Additionally, on&nbsp;<strong><span style=3D"fon=
t-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">9 October</span></strong>&nbsp;I subm=
itted a request for reimbursement of&nbsp;<strong><span style=3D"font-family=
:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">NZD 395.85</span></strong>&nbsp;for emergency=

 veterinary expenses incurred on the day of the fire. The cats required urge=
nt treatment due to prolonged smoke exposure. To date, I have not received e=
ither reimbursement or any response regarding this claim.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend">Furthermore, I currently require&nbsp;<strong><s=
pan style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">temporary storage for=
 the furniture that was salvaged</span></strong>, as I do not yet have a per=
manent place to keep these items.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend">Could you please:<o:p></o:p></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"xisselectedend" style=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1">Confirm recei=
pt of my requests<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"xisselectedend" style=3D"mso-l=
ist:l3 level1 lfo1">Process the outstanding refunds as soon as possible<o:p>=
</o:p></li><li class=3D"xisselectedend" style=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1">Ad=
vise on coverage for temporary storage<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
<p class=3D"xisselectedend">I would appreciate a prompt response, as these m=
atters remain unresolved.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p>Kind regards,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p>Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
