;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The r=
emaining amount under the temporary accommodation benefit is $13,820.62</spa=
n><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
