;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is th=
ere a time I can contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents cl=
aim? the loss schedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum in=
sured, which means that the contents
 is a total loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is g=
reater then the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this week=
 suits you.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hav=
e confirmation that your privacy request and the information you requested w=
as emailed to you on the 25/07/25. If you can check this date and let me kno=
w if you have it.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regar=
ding updates, I am more then happy to update you on the first of each month,=
 would you prefer monthly contacts from me instead of fortnightly?</span><sp=
an lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regar=
ding further claim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive the=
se from the assessor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the enti=
re claim file each month and not efficient
 for us due to the time it takes to action these we may end up getting asses=
sor reports during this process which means that report may not be added to t=
hat privacy request.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Futur=
e assessor reports should be the only documents we have that you are not giv=
en by the assessor as this would come from us.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" st=
yle=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
